game.name: Park the Beetle
game.description:
Not everyone knows how to park a car in a designed parking spot! Are you? If yes, join Park The Beetle and be prepared to drive your chosen car model to the assigned parking slot. It requires putting your intense driving and parking abilities to the test before entering the real driving simulator. There is no need to waste your time, and try to hop on the driver seat as fast as you can before it is too late.

Try to avoid all the objects and other car vehicles that you see on the road! If you hit with any of them, you will lose your game immediately. There are multiple interesting levels, incredibly realistic graphics, and different car models to choose from in this brand new addictive racing game. Perform different parking missions successfully to show off the world that you are a professional car parker. Make sure that your cars are parked in a proper position in each level.

Keep your car away from all the objects that you see on the road to survive until you clear all the levels! You can play this HTML5 car parking game on PCs, smartphones, tablets and iPhones and iPads. Crashing with other things 3 times will cause lose your game. Park all your cars and prove the world that you are certified for being the best driver on this planet! Check out more free parking simulator games on atmegame.com for free and have a blast without download!
